text: Marijampolė County is one of the ten counties in Lithuania. The capital is Marijampolė. On 1 July 2010, the county administration was ended. ==Municipalities== Municipalities are: Kalvarija Municipality Kazlų Rūda Municipality Marijampolė Municipality Šakiai District Municipality Vilkaviškis District Municipality ==References== Category:Counties of Lithuania
title: Marijampolė County
